Linkito.s:
return (

Linkito

A common solution to play, create, share and monetize puzzle games

Linkito is a puzzle ecosystem based on NEAR currently in developpment. Connect wires and interact with buttons to solve different types of puzzles. Create new puzzles with the game editor and share them with other players.

Key features

  • Connect and activate blocks to solve puzzles
  • Integrated editor to create new levels
  • Share & Monetize your levels
  • Multiple narrative campaigns
